n-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">1</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">、面试地点：湖北省嘉鱼县南嘉中学<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">(</span>嘉鱼县检察院斜对面<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">)<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">、时间安排：考生<st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\" month=\\\\\"5\\\\\" day=\\\\\"27\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">27</span>日</st1:chsdate>上午<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7:00</span>报到，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7:30</span>未报到视为弃权。上午<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8:00</span>开始面试。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengfugonggao/2012-05-21/8f12dc0fee8598b7e615e6f7fae5de7d.jpg\\\\\" /></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24.1pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">二、面试方式<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">1</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">、考生面试按所报职位，分时间分考场进行，考生面试的顺序以抽签形式确定。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">、面试总成绩为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100</span>分。面试结束后当场公布面试成绩，考生当场签字确认。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24.1pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-